{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"XRProjectionLayer","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebXR_Device_API\">WebXR Device API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer\"><code>XRProjectionLayer</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/fixedFoveation\"><code>fixedFoveation</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/ignoreDepthValues\"><code>ignoreDepthValues</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/textureArrayLength\"><code>textureArrayLength</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/textureHeight\"><code>textureHeight</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/textureWidth\"><code>textureWidth</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer\"><code>XRCompositionLayer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRLayer\"><code>XRLayer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for WebXR Device API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/xr\"><code>Navigator.xr</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/makeXRCompatible\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.makeXRCompatible()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRAnchor\"><code>XRAnchor</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRBoundedReferenceSpace\"><code>XRBoundedReferenceSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCPUDepthInformation\"><code>XRCPUDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRDepthInformation\"><code>XRDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRFrame\"><code>XRFrame</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSource\"><code>XRInputSource</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSourceArray\"><code>XRInputSourceArray</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSourceEvent\"><code>XRInputSourceEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSourcesChangeEvent\"><code>XRInputSourcesChangeEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRPose\"><code>XRPose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpace\"><code>XRReferenceSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpaceEvent\"><code>XRReferenceSpaceEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRRenderState\"><code>XRRenderState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRRigidTransform\"><code>XRRigidTransform</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSession\"><code>XRSession</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSessionEvent\"><code>XRSessionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSpace\"><code>XRSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSystem\"><code>XRSystem</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRView\"><code>XRView</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRViewerPose\"><code>XRViewerPose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRViewport\"><code>XRViewport</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding\"><code>XRWebGLBinding</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLDepthInformation\"><code>XRWebGLDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLLayer\"><code>XRWebGLLayer</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">secure contexts</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>XRProjectionLayer</code></strong> interface of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebXR_Device_API\">WebXR Device API</a> is a layer that fills the entire view of the observer and is refreshed close to the device's native frame rate.</p>\n<p><code>XRProjectionLayer</code> is supported by all <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSession\"><code>XRSession</code></a> objects (no <code>layers</code> feature descriptor is needed).</p>\n<p>\n  To create a new <code>XRProjectionLayer</code>, call <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createProjectionLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createProjectionLayer()</code></a>.\n  To present layers to the XR device, add them to the <code>layers</code> render state using <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSession/updateRenderState\"><code>XRSession.updateRenderState()</code></a>.\n</p>\n<p><code>XRProjectionLayer</code> objects don't have an associated <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSpace\"><code>XRSpace</code></a>, because they render to the full frame.</p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"88\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"44\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      EventTarget\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"88\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"118\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"88,14 98,9 98,19 88,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRLayer\">\n    <rect x=\"118\" y=\"0\" width=\"75\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"155.5\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      XRLayer\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"193\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"223\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"193,14 203,9 203,19 193,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer\">\n    <rect x=\"223\" y=\"0\" width=\"144\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"295\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      XRCompositionLayer\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"367\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"397\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"367,14 377,9 377,19 367,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer\" aria-current=\"page\">\n    <rect x=\"397\" y=\"0\" width=\"136\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"465\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      XRProjectionLayer\n    </text>\n  </a></svg>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Inherits properties from its parent, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer\"><code>XRCompositionLayer</code></a>.</em></p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"xrcompositionlayer.blendtexturesourcealpha\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/blendTextureSourceAlpha\"><code>XRCompositionLayer.blendTextureSourceAlpha</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A boolean enabling the layer's texture alpha channel.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrcompositionlayer.chromaticaberrationcorrection\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/chromaticAberrationCorrection\"><code>XRCompositionLayer.chromaticAberrationCorrection</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A boolean enabling optical chromatic aberration correction for the layer if the device supports it, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/null\"><code>null</code></a> otherwise.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrprojectionlayer.fixedfoveation\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/fixedFoveation\"><code>XRProjectionLayer.fixedFoveation</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A number indicating the amount of foveation used by the XR compositor for the layer. Fixed Foveated Rendering (FFR) renders the edges of the eye textures at a lower resolution than the center and reduces the GPU load.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrprojectionlayer.ignoredepthvalues\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/ignoreDepthValues\"><code>XRProjectionLayer.ignoreDepthValues</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A boolean indicating that the XR compositor is not making use of depth buffer values when rendering the layer.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrcompositionlayer.layout\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/layout\"><code>XRCompositionLayer.layout</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The layout type of the layer.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrcompositionlayer.miplevels\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/mipLevels\"><code>XRCompositionLayer.mipLevels</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The actual number of mip levels in the color and texture data for the layer.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrcompositionlayer.needsredraw\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/needsRedraw\"><code>XRCompositionLayer.needsRedraw</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A boolean signaling that the layer should be re-rendered in the next frame.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrprojectionlayer.texturearraylength\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/textureArrayLength\"><code>XRProjectionLayer.textureArrayLength</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The layer's layer count for array textures when using <code>texture-array</code> as the <code>textureType</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrprojectionlayer.textureheight\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/textureHeight\"><code>XRProjectionLayer.textureHeight</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The height in pixels of the color textures of this layer.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrprojectionlayer.texturewidth\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer/textureWidth\"><code>XRProjectionLayer.textureWidth</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The width in pixels of the color textures of this layer.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Inherits methods from its parents, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer\"><code>XRCompositionLayer</code></a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></em>.</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"eventtarget.addeventlistener\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Registers an event handler of a specific event type on the <code>EventTarget</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xrcompositionlayer.destroy\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/destroy\"><code>XRCompositionLayer.destroy()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Deletes the underlying layer attachments.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"eventtarget.dispatchevent\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent\"><code>EventTarget.dispatchEvent()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Dispatches an event to this <code>EventTarget</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"eventtarget.removeeventlistener\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/removeEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.removeEventListener()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Removes an event listener from the <code>EventTarget</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"query":"api.XRProjectionLayer","specifications":[]}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.XRProjectionLayer","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRLayer\"><code>XRLayer</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer\"><code>XRCompositionLayer</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XREquirectLayer\"><code>XREquirectLayer</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCubeLayer\"><code>XRCubeLayer</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCylinderLayer\"><code>XRCylinderLayer</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRQuadLayer\"><code>XRQuadLayer</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The XRProjectionLayer interface of the WebXR Device API is a layer that fills the entire view of the observer and is refreshed close to the device's native frame rate.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:23:40.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/xrprojectionlayer","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/xrprojectionlayer/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/073f70e052ff92ab715df3c20678c11c9b51747f","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRProjectionLayer","title":"XRProjectionLayer"}],"pageTitle":"XRProjectionLayer - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}